@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5100

### 黑名单：配置后验证 403
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 白名单：配置后验证放行
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 自动封禁：触发限流后验证 403
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 禁用限流端点：验证不受限流影响
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 配置提示
# 在 appsettings.Local.json 中按需切换：
# - RateLimit.Blacklist
# - RateLimit.Whitelist
# - RateLimit.Blacklist.AutoBlockAfterRejections
# - [DisableRateLimiting] 标注的端点
